Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.28,0:40:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.57,0:40:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双份伏特加\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two double vodkas.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.57,0:40:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-加冰和柠檬吗  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ice and lemon? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.20,0:40:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.16,0:40:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀  有刀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Knife! Knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.57,0:40:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别拘捕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.37,0:40:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.01,0:40:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.37,0:40:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.53,0:40:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.61,0:40:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.24,0:41:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我  放开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get off of me! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.28,0:41:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -不吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.13,0:41:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, isn't him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.05,0:41:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我看到了刀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I saw a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.01,0:41:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.24,0:41:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我以为他有刀  -滚出我的视线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I thought he had a knife. - Just get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.49,0:41:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  算了  你被撤掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, actually no. Stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.76,0:41:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回家去  明天也别来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sending you home, don't come in tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.28,0:41:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jo--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.09,0:41:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别喊我乔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't call me Jo!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.49,0:41:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真得退一步了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to step back from this, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.13,0:41:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是尽了职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's just done what any of us would've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.41,0:41:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对这事太动感情了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is too personal for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.57,0:41:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再也不要不接我的电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you ever, ever have your phone turned off to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.49,0:41:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你以为你在跟谁说话呢  -闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who do you think you're talking to? - Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.57,0:41:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  听好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut up and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.89,0:41:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想通过银行追踪的勒索犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The blackmailers I was trying to track through the bank....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.24,0:41:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人没能追踪到他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My contact couldn't trace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.72,0:41:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.85,0:41:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我另想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll find another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.32,0:41:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们收工吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's wrap this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.57,0:41:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但丁·甘纳森刚醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dante Gunnarsson's just come round.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.93,0:41:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我去吧  -我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let me go. I can-- - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.37,0:41:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.61,0:41:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.45,0:42:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动吉连家  我理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leaving Killane's house, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.13,0:42:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周边房子  也行  但整个工地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The surrounding houses, okay, but the whole fucking site?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.76,0:42:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止一切拆除\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stopping any demolition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.37,0:42:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我损失重大  他们根本不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is costing me a fortune. They have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.89,0:42:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是什么外人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not like I'm some kind of an outsider or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.45,0:42:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的街道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was my street.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.89,0:42:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉连夫妇曾是我的朋友  曾经也是好朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Killanes were friends. They were good friends once.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.53,0:42:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  出于尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, due respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.97,0:42:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是最能理解的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand better than anyone here,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.68,0:42:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能停止整个施工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you don't close down the whole operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.61,0:42:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.85,0:42:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是报复  太武断了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vindictive! It was arbitrary!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.24,0:42:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个负责的女警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That police woman in charge...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.01,0:42:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,态度傲慢  我见过太多次了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's an attitude. I've seen it so many times before!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.05,0:42:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I kid you not,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.85,0:42:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是不放过一切让你难受的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they will take any opportunity to kick you where it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.13,0:42:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-柯琳失踪了  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Corinne's missing. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.65,0:42:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯琳失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said Corinne's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.09,0:42:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's gone. She...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.76,0:42:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经走了六天了  我不知道她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's been gone for about six days. I don't know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.89,0:42:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你怎么没说  -我这不说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why didn't you say? - I'm saying it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.28,0:42:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好吧  -我需要问你件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay. - Look, I need to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.28,0:42:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不知道你是推动此事的公司的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know you owned the company behind this,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.32,0:42:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但你说吉连知道  -是的  我都说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- but you think Killane did, right? - Yeah, I said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.97,0:42:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得那是他雇我的原因吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you think that's why he hired me,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.28,0:42:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他以为那能阻止你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because he thought it might stop you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.85,0:42:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  可能的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, it's feasible.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.80,0:43:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那跟柯琳有什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But what would that have to do with Corinne?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.32,0:43:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他还绑架了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe he got to her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.93,0:43:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.65,0:43:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前在帮我找她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}helping me look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.49,0:43:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直跟我扯什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kept spouting all this bullshit
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.89,0:43:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些女人走了就不回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about sometimes women leave and they don't come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.93,0:43:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果一直以来  他自己的老婆...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and all the time his own wife was...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.53,0:43:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还骗了我什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What else has he been lying to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.13,0:43:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他知道什么关于柯琳的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think he knows something about Corinne
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.41,0:43:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that he's not telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.53,0:43:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得找他谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.53,0:43:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.01,0:43:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警探\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.32,0:43:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why? What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.05,0:43:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪家医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.32,0:43:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.16,0:43:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.41,0:43:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马丁·吉连刚企图自杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Martin Killane just tried to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.41,0:43:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.85,0:44:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  你不能进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, you're not allowed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.28,0:44:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得找他问问我妻子的事  他之前在帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just need to talk to him about my wife. He was helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.61,0:44:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被打了麻药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's sedated.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.05,0:44:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈上晚课\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom does evening classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.49,0:44:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数学和生物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maths and biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.32,0:44:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她想做个护士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She wants to be a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.05,0:44:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等到她走了才来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I waited till she went.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.93,0:44:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就像你妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're like your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.49,0:44:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.65,0:44:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她担心我经常生病的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's been worried about me being ill so often,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.90,0:44:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很好心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you're kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.28,0:44:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.24,0:44:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还问我要不要再去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She even asked if I wanted to see
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.68,0:44:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找别的医生看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}another doctor for a second opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.37,0:44:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈不想那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, my mom didn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.37,0:44:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就没去  但\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we didn't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.16,0:44:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她真是好心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it was nice of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.89,0:44:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么经常生病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you ill so often?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.93,0:44:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.57,0:44:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你都在服什么药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But what medication are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.13,0:44:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈负责那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mom does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.53,0:44:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.13,0:45:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗生素和治恶心的药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Antibiotics and stuff for nausea.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.01,0:45:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么是谁在服那么多药  你妈妈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, so who takes all the medicine around here? Your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.57,0:45:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.37,0:45:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.01,0:45:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想谈埃拉和迈克的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, look, I wanted to talk about Ella and Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.05,0:45:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会说到那个的  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will, but listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.13,0:45:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听你妈妈撒谎说你在医院后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After your mom said you were in hospital and you weren't,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.72,0:45:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到她丢掉了大量的处方药盒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we saw her throwing out these boxes of prescription drugs,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.93,0:45:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有好多盒老鼠药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and even boxes of rat poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.57,0:45:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不是扔在你们自家垃圾箱里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And not in your own bin.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.28,0:45:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.65,0:45:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's my mom.
